race_name: Busch Light Clash at The Coliseum
race_comments: .Joey Logano has won the 2022 Busch Light Clash at the Colisem at the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum, his second career victory in the annual non-points exhibition NASCAR Cup Series race.
